Class Dancer

  • java.lang.Object
    • cafedansadatabase.Dancer

  • public class Dancer
extends java.lang.Object
    Dancer.java Data Type describing a dancer with various information attached to it. These Dancer objects will be used to populate the database in our application. 
        Project: CafeDansa Database
    Platform: jdk 1.8.0_14; NetBeans IDE 8.1; Windows 10
    Course: CS 143
    Created on Apr 5, 2016, 1:26:19 PM
    Revised on Arp 12, 2016, 2:30:21 PM
